==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hollygrape
<hw>hollygrape</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An ornamental evergreen shrub
(<spn>Mahonia aquifolium</spn>) of the Pacific coast of North America
having dark green pinnate leaves and racemes of yellow flowers followed
by blue-black berries.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Oregon grape, Oregon holly grape, mountain grape,
holly-leaves barberry, <spn>Mahonia aquifolium</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hollyhock</ent>⟦br⟧
